node.title: Six Covid-19 cases linked to Auckland parlour, visitors urged to get tested
node.description: An Auckland massage parlour has become the focus of multiple exposure events for Covid-19.
node.content:
["An Auckland massage parlour has become the focus of multiple exposure events for Covid-19.", "", "
Pelican club in Eden Terrace, Auckland. Photo: Google Maps
", "So far, six infected people have been linked to the Pelican Club in Eden Terrace.", "The Northern Regional Health Coordination Centre said anyone who was at the premises between 22 December and 31 Friday, should isolate at home for 10 days after their visit, regardless of whether they have symptoms.", "It said if symptoms did develop, they should get an additional test and remain at home until all test results come back negative.", "Staff at the Pelican Club are being advised by the manager on what action to take.", "There were 27 new community cases of the coronavirus reported today."]
